<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-6"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <!-- Header -->
  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <!-- Problema pasticceria -->
    <div class="p-4 md:p-6 bg-white border-3 border-cyan-500 rounded-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-bold text-cyan-700 mb-4">In pasticceria</h2>

      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 mb-6">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <p class="text-gray-800 mb-3">In pasticceria il papà di Barbara ordina il dolce al cioccolato per 2 bambini e il dolce alla frutta per 4 bambini.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-800 font-bold">Quanto spenderà il papà di Barbara?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p072/p072_01.jpg", alt: "Listino prezzi pasticceria", class: "max-w-xs rounded-lg" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 mb-4" data-controller="fill-blanks">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-pink-600 font-bold">–</span> Il testo contiene tutte le informazioni per risolvere il problema?</span>
          <button class="px-4 py-1 border-2 border-cyan-300 rounded hover:bg-cyan-100">Sì</button>
          <button class="px-4 py-1 border-2 border-cyan-300 rounded hover:bg-cyan-100">No</button>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-pink-600 font-bold">–</span> Quali informazioni mancano?</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-full mt-2 px-3 py-2 border-2 border-cyan-300 rounded focus:border-cyan-500 focus:outline-none" placeholder="Scrivi la risposta...">
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-pink-600 font-bold">–</span> L'immagine contiene le informazioni che mancano nel testo?</span>
          <button class="px-4 py-1 border-2 border-cyan-300 rounded hover:bg-cyan-100">Sì</button>
          <button class="px-4 py-1 border-2 border-cyan-300 rounded hover:bg-cyan-100">No</button>
        </div>
        <div class="p-3 bg-cyan-50 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-gray-800"><strong>Risposta:</strong> Il papà di Barbara spenderà
            <input type="text" class="w-24 px-2 py-1 border-2 border-cyan-300 rounded focus:border-cyan-500 focus:outline-none text-center font-bold" data-fill-blanks-target="input" placeholder="...">
            euro.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Problema grafico spese -->
    <div class="p-4 md:p-6 bg-white border-3 border-blue-500 rounded-3xl">
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4"><span class="text-pink-600">&#8226;</span> Sul grafico è rappresentato l'andamento delle spese della famiglia Bianchi dell'anno scorso.</p>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-pink-600 font-bold">–</span> In quale mese la famiglia Bianchi ha speso di più?</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-40 px-3 py-2 border-2 border-blue-300 rounded focus:border-blue-500 focus:outline-none">
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-pink-600 font-bold">–</span> In quale ha speso di meno?</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-40 px-3 py-2 border-2 border-blue-300 rounded focus:border-blue-500 focus:outline-none">
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-pink-600 font-bold">–</span> Quanti euro ha speso in un anno intero?</span>
          <input type="text" class="w-40 px-3 py-2 border-2 border-blue-300 rounded focus:border-blue-500 focus:outline-none">
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-pink-600 font-bold">–</span> A metà anno era già stata spesa la metà della spesa annuale?</span>
          <button class="px-4 py-1 border-2 border-blue-300 rounded hover:bg-blue-100">Sì</button>
          <button class="px-4 py-1 border-2 border-blue-300 rounded hover:bg-blue-100">No</button>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-pink-600 font-bold">–</span> Secondo te, perché la famiglia ha speso di più ad agosto e a dicembre?</span>
          <textarea class="w-full mt-2 px-3 py-2 border-2 border-blue-300 rounded focus:border-blue-500 focus:outline-none" rows="2"></textarea>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Problema parallelogramma -->
    <div class="p-4 md:p-6 bg-white border-3 border-green-500 rounded-3xl">
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4"><span class="text-pink-600">&#8226;</span> Il disegno rappresenta il cortile di una scuola: calcola l'area.</p>

      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-4">
          <div>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><span class="text-pink-600 font-bold">–</span> Come si calcola l'area del parallelogramma?</span>
            <input type="text" class="w-full mt-2 px-3 py-2 border-2 border-green-300 rounded focus:border-green-500 focus:outline-none">
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><span class="text-pink-600 font-bold">–</span> Osservando il disegno puoi trovare le misure necessarie:</p>
            <div class="space-y-3 ml-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="text-gray-700">misura della base del parallelogramma:</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-20 px-2 py-1 border-2 border-green-300 rounded focus:border-green-500 focus:outline-none text-center">
                <span class="text-gray-700">m</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="text-gray-700">misura dell'altezza del parallelogramma:</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-20 px-2 py-1 border-2 border-green-300 rounded focus:border-green-500 focus:outline-none text-center">
                <span class="text-gray-700">m</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="text-gray-700">misura dell'area del parallelogramma:</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-2 border-green-300 rounded focus:border-green-500 focus:outline-none text-center">
                <span class="text-gray-700">m ×</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-2 border-green-300 rounded focus:border-green-500 focus:outline-none text-center">
                <span class="text-gray-700">m =</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-16 px-2 py-1 border-2 border-green-300 rounded focus:border-green-500 focus:outline-none text-center">
                <span class="text-gray-700">m²</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p072/p072_02.jpg", alt: "Parallelogramma cortile", class: "max-w-xs rounded-lg" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Exercise Controls -->
    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls', color: 'blue' %>
  </div>
</div>
